==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Recoct
<hw>Re*coct"</hw> <pr>(r⟦esl⟧*k⟦ocr⟧kt")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>recoctus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>recoquere</ets> to cook or boil over
again. See <er>Re-</er>, and 4th <er>Cook</er>.]</ety> <def>To boil or
cook again; hence, to make over; to vamp up; to reconstruct.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

